    <h2>Why Choose Wired Open Ear Headphones Instead of Wireless?</h2>
    <p>Wireless headphones are popular, but they aren’t always practical. Wired open ear headphones solve many everyday problems.</p>

    <h3>Zero Audio Lag</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>No delay during calls</li>
      <li>No lip-sync issues while watching videos</li>
      <li>No lag during gaming or meetings</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Ideal for work-from-home users, students, gamers, and professionals.</p>

    <h3>No Charging, No Battery Stress</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>No charging cycles</li>
      <li>No battery degradation</li>
      <li>No sudden shutdown mid-call</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Just plug in and use — anytime.</p>

    <h3>Stable & Reliable Sound</h3>
    <p>No pairing errors or signal drops. Wired open ear earphones deliver consistent audio even in crowded environments.</p>

    <h3>Safer Listening</h3>
    <p>Because your ears stay open, you can hear traffic, conversations, and alerts — making them safer than traditional wired earbuds.</p>
  </section>

